A binary qualitative data matrix was constructed and analyzed using POPGENE Version 1.3.2. Genetic diversity of different materials was determined by calculating the percentage of polymorphic bands (PPB), the effective number of alleles (Ne), observed number of alleles (Na), Nei’s gene diversity (H), and Shannon’s information index (I). The polymorphic information (PIC) of a band was calculated by the following formula: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
