				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{PIC}=1-\sum \limits_j^i{P_{ij}}^2 $$\end{document}PIC=1−∑jiPij2 (Pi and Pj are the frequencies of the ith and jth alleles at one locus). We used the software NTSYS Version 2.1 [49] to construct a cluster analysis description of selected group Q pattern based on Nei’s genetic distances [50]. Afterwards, the unweighted pairwise method of arithmetic mean is used to analyze the parameters.
